Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:04.98,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you call me out here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.32,0:00:08.23,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we could check \Nanswers, like we promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:10.44,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find out what future \Ncourse Yukino-chan picked?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.50,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I do know, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:14.94,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But it wouldn't be fair for \Nme to be the one to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.45,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how dutiful of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:21.20,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,But I see... So she actually told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:25.20,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yukino-chan really trusts you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:27.51,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't call it trust...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:29.73,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's what it is, in my case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:32.19,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you do realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:35.79,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. It's not trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:37.59,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's something much more cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:41.76,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:44.92,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,And she thinks it's fine that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:47.86,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's part of what makes \Nher so cute, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.15,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's what I can't stand about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:53.78,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not trust, then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:55.19,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Who can say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.19,0:00:58.53,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,But at the very least, \NI wouldn't call it the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:00.53,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Those were your words, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:05.41,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Does that "real thing" even exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:14.51,Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(235,1)}My Teen\NRomantic\NComedy\N{\c&H8D39E0&}SNAFU\N{\c&HDCA02E&}TOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.55,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:43.32,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eat something sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:44.58,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.68,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wanna eat a little chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:47.34,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:48.93,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Get it? A little chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:50.86,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's almost that time, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:54.31,Ore_Main,Ohoka,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine, Hayato-kun, \Nbut we're in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:55.71,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:59.30,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato-kun doesn't usually \Naccept Valentine's chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.29,Ore_Main,Ohoka,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:01.78,Ore_Main,Ohoka,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:06.78,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,But it's kinda scary getting it from \Nsomeone you don't know well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.08,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, giving handmade is kinda heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:12.98,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I can understand why he \Nwouldn't accept those.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.07,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:15.09,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.09,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:29.77,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Handmade, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:39.46,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you leave first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:42.16,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I never said I'd go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:45.20,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.76,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You stayed in the classroom for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:51.47,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just checking out how \NHayama and Miura were doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:54.21,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Yeah. I think they're okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:58.05,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,That kinda thing is nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:01.20,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they really treasure \Nwhat they have right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.25,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Like the present time is the best time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:04.16,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.24,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the present time is the best time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:09.97,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's unusually \Noptimistic of you, Hikki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:13.05,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Recalling the past dredges up \Nregrets that make me want to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:15.47,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,and when I think of the future, \Nthe anxiety just makes me depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.73,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,By process of elimination, you could \Nsay right now is my happiest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.73,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It was pessimistic after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.30,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You're so quick to say stuff like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.73,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you... have any free days coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:35.72,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... Um, probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:38.63,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty much free... I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.80,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.14,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.14,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yahello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.64,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:57.65,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And again, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:04:59.65,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:03.15,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,not that it matters, but do you like sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:06.72,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I think Hayama would be glad \Nto eat anything you give him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:11.28,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,But they were saying Hayato-kun \Ndoesn't accept chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:13.18,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.51,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.67,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Because it would cause arguments, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.74,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,In grade school, the mood in the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.67,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,classroom the following \Nday was always strained.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.89,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then I guess you'll do, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:29.02,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:30.61,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the right way to ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:31.70,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Hikki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:33.68,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,does like sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.35,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:39.23,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure why you two \Nanswered that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.61,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.18,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:45.36,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sure how sweet I should make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:48.61,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has different tastes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:52.94,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,How sweet? Are you planning \Non making your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:53.78,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:54.99,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it surprising?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:57.50,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really good at making sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.39,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, so I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:01.75,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I could use you as a reference \Nto make obligatory chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.48,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Obligatory, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:06.88,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you one of those guys who's \Nnever gotten chocolate before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:08.72,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Hikki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.32,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,will get chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:13.35,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.73,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:21.31,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.57,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I've got Komachi, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.58,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Komachi? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:26.27,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,The rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:27.38,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,She's not rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:30.32,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Komachi-chan is Hikki's little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:31.95,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Sister complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:32.95,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:35.34,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I can deny that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:38.50,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,So you do like younger girls, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:40.46,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:44.81,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, since your birthday's in April, \Nthere's less than a year between us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:47.06,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't really think \Nof you as younger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:50.45,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:51.55,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.60,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I was just a little surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.14,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, scary! Why do you know her birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.99,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,That's creepy, Hikki! Seriously creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:00.60,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly know her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.82,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, Isshiki said it herself the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.73,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,when the little sneak was trying \Nto look pointlessly appealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.86,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Pointlessly?! It wasn't pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:10.59,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not a sneak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:13.04,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,You're a bigger sneak than I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:16.12,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,How do I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:20.24,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try making chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:23.65,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be studying for exams next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:28.09,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,So I figured I could at least try it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:31.27,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yumiko, didn't you say giving \Nhandmade is kinda heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:33.51,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:37.12,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I think handmade is a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.81,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hikitani-kun, why don't you make friendship \Nchocolate for Hayato-kun, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.51,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:43.56,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't accept chocolate anyway, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.68,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if it's between boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:47.23,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What you're assuming is not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.21,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:53.10,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,If he says he won't accept \Nany, that makes it tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.41,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:59.40,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes, they're scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.46,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:09.21,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Er... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.93,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I wasn't done talking yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:15.06,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're just drinking tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:15.72,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.06,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.72,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Sakisaki, you had something \Nto say, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.76,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell us about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:24.81,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Well... It's about chocolate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:27.83,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,You want to give someone chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.00,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:29.54,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:30.19,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:33.70,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Look, could you stop assuming I'm like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:34.49,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:35.41,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.71,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Please play nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:39.24,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.78,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What about chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.67,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,My sister said she wants to make some.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:46.00,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a kind that even \Na little kid can make?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.95,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,That even a little kid can make...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:51.92,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,But, Sakisaki, aren't you good at housework?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:56.62,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,The stuff I make is sort of plain...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:58.68,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure a little kid would like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:01.38,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,What kinds of things can you make, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:05.70,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Sim—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:07.44,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,S—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.19,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Simmered taro balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.19,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.94,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I think that sounds nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:19.78,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I can't cook at all, \Nso I think that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.14,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you, Yukinon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:21.99,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:25.43,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,"Nikkorogashi" sounds a \Nbit like "nekkorogashi,"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:27.37,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,so it sounds rather cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.69,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,That was a weird comment to follow up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.34,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Cats have nothing to do with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.47,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite a problem, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:40.07,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's kind of a problem that \NMiura-senpai seems to be serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:43.35,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking about the number of \Nrequests for help we've received.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:47.10,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of understand how \NHayato-kun feels, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:51.10,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:54.94,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It would probably give me all kinds \Nof weird ideas about stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:58.55,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... That sounds like you, Yui-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:01.24,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You... think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.53,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:09.33,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, wouldn't you just need an excuse, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:12.53,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Like, a front that's convincing to Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:13.34,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.23,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If he has no choice but to accept them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:17.84,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Or if the situation makes it \Nnatural for him to accept them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.16,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,it's a different story, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:20.94,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:23.31,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,you mean she just needs to have an excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:27.67,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,For example, instead of \Nsaying it's for Valentine's,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:30.23,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,if you just ask him to taste-test \Nit, he'd probably eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.65,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Probably. Not that I'd know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:36.53,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! We should make some together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.79,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:41.35,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be like an event for all \Nof us who came with requests,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.97,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,where Yukinoshita-senpai can \Nteach all of us how to make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:48.46,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes... That would be fine with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:53.01,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Vice President? I'm gonna \Nneed a project proposal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:53.94,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:55.51,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Yuigahama-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.47,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You can make some with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:00.24,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You don't trust me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:03.55,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, then what should Hikki do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.11,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:07.31,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.56,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You can taste them and give your opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.32,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I can do. It's my best subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.82,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:16.73,honmoku,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Honmoku Makito
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:19.99,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, I'll handle the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:23.00,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a cooking class!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.53,commcenter,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Chiba City Mihama Ward Takasu Community Center
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.04,almostvalday_11:24,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Almost Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.04,cookingclass,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking Class
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.04,information,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Information
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.04,no min req,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Inexperienced cooks welcome!\NNo minimum requirements!\NVery at-home atmosphere!\NGain the experience and know-how\Nto be independent in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:28.38,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the reaction to our \Nlast event was great,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.96,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,and it generated a lot of buzz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:33.22,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can continue working \Nin alliance from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:34.53,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:38.42,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You guys are here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:41.06,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:44.54,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think I had a \Nlog of it in our emails...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.14,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? You look way too cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.64,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Pres, we'd like to get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.36,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.74,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,This is a business chance, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:57.17,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We can use crowd funding to raise funds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:57.17,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.18,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,It's best if we can make this a joint effort
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:01.28,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and pull some of the budget from them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:04.78,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,And luckily for me, it saves me \Nthe cost of obligatory chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.58,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.53,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that idea aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:11.51,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You're more impressive than \NI thought, Isshiki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:14.10,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yahello!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:15.46,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.53,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:21.81,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this is today's special \Ninstructor, Haru-san-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:23.97,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! I'm Haru-san-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:26.66,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you ask her to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:29.64,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she seems like a total \Nveteran at this stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.15,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I would have been sufficient on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:35.65,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Cut up the chocolate and \Nwarm it with hot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:38.73,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Then let it cool and pour it into molds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.32,Ore_Main,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.91,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Well, basically, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.45,Ore_Main,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... That seems kinda easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.85,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You're naïve, Yumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:49.14,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Warming it with hot water doesn't \Nmean you put it {\i1}in{\i0} hot water!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:52.50,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You do it more like this! Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.75,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't mind me bringing her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.50,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see a problem with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:00.33,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.67,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan, what kind of candy would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:04.59,Ore_Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Eel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.64,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:08.90,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:13.52,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,O-Our family had eel the other \Nday, and she really liked it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:17.77,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,In other countries, it's common \Nfor men to give the gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:20.68,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should focus on \Nthat sort of globalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.53,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You really thought this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:25.03,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,This way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:26.95,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,they can all act natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:31.52,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,It's even made Tobe happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:32.20,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:35.20,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about chocolate or Tobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.25,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Tobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.10,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,That's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:39.86,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:51.06,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.07,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Are you hitting on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:56.13,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,If you think whispering sweet nothings \Nwill work because I'm making sweets,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.73,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,then you're being naïve. \NYou're gonna have to try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:13:59.90,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.19,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:08.07,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, do you dislike \Nsweet things like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:15.08,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you'd call it a difference in \Nawareness between Japan and other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.83,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Hikigaya, got any extra chocolate molds?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:22.54,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:25.84,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:30.30,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \Ndid I ever give you chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:33.89,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.39,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:37.89,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you some this year, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:40.15,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Er... Uh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:45.48,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of, Yukino-chan gave \Nyou chocolate once, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.94,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.41,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Right before we started grade school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.54,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,she gave some to both you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:08.93,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,So, who are you giving yours to, Yukino-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:11.22,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see what that has to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.18,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't say you're \Nnot giving it to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:15.76,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}are{\i0} giving it to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:21.21,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are only so many \Npeople you could give it to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:25.15,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,This is nonsense. Say whatever you wan—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.64,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:33.66,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:36.20,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she all flustered?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.79,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing her like that is gonna \Nmake me flustered, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.90,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get flustered...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:48.55,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You've still got a way \Nto go yourself, Yukinon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:52.68,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a master at handling \Nbowls and cooking utensils!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:56.58,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's the rest of it that \Nyou're fatally flawed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:47.09,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,This turned out to be a great event.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:49.67,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's an event I \Ndon't really get, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.45,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,That's just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:54.03,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,You're a guy who doesn't \Nreally get much, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:57.51,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,The people you're involved with \Nwith don't get much, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:59.26,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural it would turn out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.46,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Saying I don't get much is kinda mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:05.62,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you understand a \Nlittle more now than you used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:08.54,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Your impressions of people \Nare renewed every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:10.53,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,As you spend time with them
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:13.47,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and grow with them, \Nyou come to understand more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:15.89,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't particularly feel like I've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:18.43,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I always keep doing the same things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:23.08,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,When you're walking, you don't look \Nback at the distance you've covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:26.90,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, from the viewpoint \Nof someone who stopped walking,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:30.99,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,the more distance they've covered, \Nthe more betrayed they feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:35.70,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I got to see all \Nof this up close now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:39.59,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Because I won't be able \Nto watch you guys forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:48.80,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Hikki! Try these!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.46,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:56.91,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're preparing \Nfor the worst, but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.98,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I made them with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:00.93,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a relief, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.89,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say something really mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:09.62,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:11.98,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:13.77,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:18.74,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the "real thing" \Nyou were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:25.00,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Are times like these your "real thing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:27.50,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:30.32,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:32.63,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you're that kind of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.36,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:39.63,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If I were interesting, I'd be \Nthe most loved guy in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:41.76,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I like that side of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:45.25,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,But the way you guys are being now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:47.27,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,is kind of boring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:51.27,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I liked you better before, Yukino-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:59.30,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just not used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:01.62,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I've never experienced it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:05.84,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it just felt a little \Nawkward because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:11.46,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd get used to it, \Nand eventually accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:16.84,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But you just wouldn't \Noverlook that awkwardness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:20.09,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,The student council will handle the \Nrest, so you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:23.29,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,We'll still help out until it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:26.10,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There's no need for any reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:27.60,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:30.02,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll take you up on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:36.51,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinoshita Haruno attacks me with the things
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:38.82,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,that I've always tried not to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:42.23,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:43.99,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's something more cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:46.33,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Something repulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:02.02,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Mom? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:06.15,Ore_Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno told me about the \Nfuture course you've chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:13.52,Ore_Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yukino, what have you been \Ndoing until this late hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:19.40,Ore_Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were a child who \Nwouldn't do these sorts of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:24.79,Ore_Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I let you live your own life \Nbecause I trusted you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:28.70,Ore_Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,No. This is my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.18,Ore_Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It was my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:34.58,Ore_Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Was it my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.79,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:40.30,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,There was a student council event \Ntoday, and... we were helping...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:43.15,Ore_Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I see. And you were walking her home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.50,Ore_Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:49.84,Ore_Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're out too late, I'm sure \Nyour family will worry, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:50.56,Ore_Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:02.07,Ore_Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to live your own life, \Nand be who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:05.82,Ore_Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm worried that you'll \Ntake the wrong path.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:08.33,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:10.83,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,So please, go home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:17.07,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Who she is... Who I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:21.73,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's some part of us \Nthat's pre-determined by others,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:23.92,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,and that part is always a bit off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:25.93,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:31.17,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But who, exactly, decides "who" that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:36.71,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I'm gonna head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:38.31,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I'll walk you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:39.48,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:42.48,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like it wouldn't be fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.36,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:57.25,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,"Who we are" is always \Nclashing with us somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:01.31,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So where is the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:04.36,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Where is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:08.89,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Still, The Thing He Seeks Is Out of Reach, \NAnd He Continues to Mistake What's Real.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:07.45,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,the real "us"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:24:08.26,Next_Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,#13 Spring, Bound Beneath the Thick Snow, Begins to Sprout.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:41.32,Ore_Main_Top,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.92,0:23:44.90,Ore_Main_Top,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not smart or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:46.17,Ore_Main_Top,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,and it wouldn't be fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.91,0:23:48.97,Ore_Main_Top,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one answer for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.91,0:23:53.83,Ore_Main_Top,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure it's not the answer \Nthat everyone else wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:58.90,Ore_Main_Top,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,What I desire and what's \Ndesired of me are so similar,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.61,0:24:02.34,Ore_Main_Top,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,so why are they so different?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.32,0:24:04.32,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.89,0:24:06.81,Ore_Main_Top,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I wouldn't \Ncare if it was a lie...
